---
title: Gochujang Bacon Fried Rice with Charred Bok Choy
description: We're channeling Korean flavours in this quick and dirty fried rice. Charred bok choy adds a subtle smokiness and gochujang provides  the perfect amount of heat and sweetness that play so well with everyone's favourite...bacon!
